Do you blame others for a mistake?
Don't blame others if you haven't finished something in time, you forgot to send an important letter or message!
Do not allude to the chaos that eventually prevails in the office, nor to the noise that your colleagues make!
You must recognize if you have made a mistake that harms others and you must repair the fault!
Ask how you can repair your fault!
Do you feel too much at home in the office?
Jogging and slippers: very comfortable room for the house, but not suitable for the office!
Don't see a comfortable jogging even if your occupation allows it!
Don't be unruly, respect your colleagues and yourself by wearing everyday, elegant and beautiful clothes when your occupation demands it!
